    "body": "Yes agreed this would be better UX. \r\n\r\nSome thought is required in how to do this correctly. The Validator client is very lightweight and does not contain information about chain state etc, it relies on the beacon node via the HTTP. \r\n\r\nFor a number of reasons, we don't activate the HTTP server until genesis is known (a few days before a network launches). So adjusting this logic to accommodate validator clients running before a known genesis requires some thought.",
